@startuml pattern_singleton
title Singleton Pattern - Head Lab Coordinator

class HeadLabCoordinator {
  -INSTANCE: HeadLabCoordinator
  -HeadLabCoordinator()
  +getInstance(): HeadLabCoordinator
  +loginMatches(email,password): boolean
  +autoGenerateManager(...): User
}

class LoginFrame
class HeadCoordinatorFrame
class User

LoginFrame --> HeadLabCoordinator : getInstance().loginMatches()
HeadCoordinatorFrame --> HeadLabCoordinator : getInstance().autoGenerateManager()
HeadLabCoordinator --> User : create manager account

note right of HeadLabCoordinator
Req2: exactly one coordinator authority
end note

@enduml
